{"tid":1322484,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"唔好顧住還拖，大家要諗返五大訴求","createTime":"2019-07-16T03:01:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-16T04:31:47.000Z","uid":146813,"like":27,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"204a075af0edef158175f15f001a26dd2d6e4b2d","tid":1322484,"uid":146813,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T03:01:40.000Z","msg":"我地721主要目的<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">唔係打狗</span><br />\n係<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">五大訴求</span><br />\n要打都<span style=\"color: purple;\">唔好做先出手果個</span><br />\n唔好teamkill, 唔好死人<br />\n<br />\n見到有d post 講要主動攻仲要勁多正皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n希望大家停一停諗一諗，你打狗既目的係乜野<br />\n721 出去既目的係乜野<br />\n文宣組唔係次次都可以推大家去上風<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n注意安全<br />\n拜託大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我唔係要分化割蓆，希望大家明白，我係和理非，但我都支持勇武，但希望大家唔好盲衝還拖，雖然都預左比人負皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frownsmile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5739563bee6585c01fc4a41f073a69d36baa3a8a","tid":1322484,"uid":146813,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T03:02:04.000Z","msg":"十連無難度"},{"pid":"17f49ff8aa0eda36b36878ae51ce9bae9f02ff92","tid":1322484,"uid":146813,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T03:02:14.000Z","msg":"二<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3160116b7b6182deabf26412a25def7a02cac51f","tid":1322484,"uid":146813,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T03:02:24.000Z","msg":"三<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3096f2b9666178243be9f8cf1fe64b95c76b8536","tid":1322484,"uid":146813,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T03:02:34.000Z","msg":"四<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ec51ae5e976297428de4c1415e5a4adadf0faa0","tid":1322484,"uid":146813,"like":0,"dislike":1,"